# Logo files

Required:

- sghub-logo.svg          (full logo, used in titlebar/marketing)
- sghub-mark.svg          (square mark, used as app icon, 1024×1024 source)
- sghub-mark-mono.svg     (monochrome variant for dark backgrounds)

If creating an app-icon set, also produce:
- sghub-mark.png at 32 / 128 / 128@2x / 256 / 512 / 1024 px
- sghub-mark.ico (Windows)
- sghub-mark.icns (macOS)
